.SH NAME
hw_enable_wol \- enable Wake-on-LAN
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" hw_enable_wol
.BI "(struct ksz_hw *hw "  ","
.BI "u32 wol_enable "  ","
.BI "const u8 *net_addr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hw" 12
The hardware instance.
.IP "wol_enable" 12
The Wake-on-LAN settings.
.IP "net_addr" 12
The IPv4 address assigned to the device.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This routine is used to enable Wake-on-LAN depending on driver settings.
